reviewText: I purchased this dvd for my 5 year old daughter and she absolutely loves it! It has 154 minutes of Sonic and a variety of episodes. Ships very quickly,  great price!
It's a winner for Sonic fans!
My great-great grandson loves this DVD.  He has watched it many times since we got it for him.  He is 5 years old.

My 3 year old son has recently discovered Sonic and will watch the same episode all day everyday if I gave him the chance. At least this variety pack isn't quite as annoying as hearing the Sonic Underground theme every 20 minutes.
Quick delivery, and great for the price! My son wanted a Sonic DVD and this was perfect. Had several episodes on it.  My son loves it!
I am very happy with this product as well how quick I received it. My son loves Sonic the Hedgehog.
Great selection of Sonic shows. Great for any child who loves Sonic!
NEED TO CHANGE SHIPPING ADDRESS ASAP

My daughters love this dvd.  The girls say the shows are funny.  Episodes on this disc are:  Spaceman Sonic, The Little Merhog, Fast & Easy, Underground Masquerade, Sonic Tonic, Ultra Sonic, and Super Sonic.
